component.name: org.nuxeo.apidoc.doctypeContrib
component.xmlFileContent:
<?xml version="1.0"?>
<component name="org.nuxeo.apidoc.doctypeContrib">

  <extension target="org.nuxeo.ecm.core.schema.TypeService" point="doctype">

    <doctype name="NXDistribution" extends="Folder">
      <schema name="common" />
      <schema name="dublincore" />
      <schema name="file" />
      <schema name="nxdistribution" />

      <facet name="Commentable" />
      <facet name="Versionable" />
      <facet name="Folderish" />

      <subtypes>
        <type>NXBundleGroup</type>
        <type>NXBundle</type>
        <type>NXOperation</type>
        <type>Workspace</type>
      </subtypes>
    </doctype>

    <doctype name="NXBundleGroup" extends="Folder">
      <schema name="common" />
      <schema name="dublincore" />
      <schema name="file" />
      <schema name="nxbundlegroup" />

      <facet name="Commentable" />
      <facet name="Versionable" />
      <facet name="Folderish" />

      <subtypes>
        <type>NXBundleGroup</type>
      </subtypes>
    </doctype>


    <doctype name="NXBundle" extends="OrderedFolder">
      <schema name="common" />
      <schema name="dublincore" />
      <schema name="file" />
      <schema name="nxbundle" />
      <facet name="Commentable" />
      <facet name="Versionable" />
      <facet name="Folderish" />
      <subtypes>
        <type>NXComponent</type>
        <type>NXService</type>
        <type>NXExtensionPoint</type>
        <type>NXContribution</type>
      </subtypes>
    </doctype>

    <doctype name="NXComponent" extends="OrderedFolder">
      <schema name="common" />
      <schema name="dublincore" />
      <schema name="file" />
      <schema name="nxcomponent" />
      <facet name="Commentable" />
      <facet name="Versionable" />
      <facet name="Folderish" />
      <subtypes>
        <type>NXService</type>
        <type>NXExtensionPoint</type>
        <type>NXContribution</type>
      </subtypes>
    </doctype>

    <doctype name="NXExtensionPoint" extends="OrderedFolder">
      <schema name="common" />
      <schema name="dublincore" />
      <schema name="file" />
      <schema name="nxextensionpoint" />
      <schema name="apidoccommon" />

      <facet name="Commentable" />
      <facet name="Versionable" />
      <facet name="Folderish" />
    </doctype>

    <doctype name="NXContribution" extends="Document">
      <schema name="common" />
      <schema name="dublincore" />
      <schema name="file" />
      <schema name="nxcontribution" />
      <schema name="apidoccommon" />

      <facet name="Commentable" />
      <facet name="Versionable" />
    </doctype>

    <doctype name="NXService" extends="Document">
      <schema name="common" />
      <schema name="dublincore" />
      <schema name="file" />
      <schema name="nxservice" />

      <facet name="Commentable" />
      <facet name="Versionable" />
    </doctype>

    <doctype name="NXOperation" extends="Document">
      <schema name="common" />
      <schema name="dublincore" />
      <schema name="file" />

      <schema name="nxoperation" />
      <facet name="Commentable" />
      <facet name="Versionable" />
    </doctype>

    <doctype name="NXDocumentation" extends="Document">
      <schema name="common" />
      <schema name="dublincore" />
      <schema name="file" />
      <schema name="files" />
      <schema name="nxdocumentation" />
      <facet name="Commentable" />
      <facet name="Versionable" />
    </doctype>

  </extension>

</component>

component.name: org.nuxeo.apidoc.listener.contrib
component.xmlFileContent:
<?xml version="1.0"?>
<component name="org.nuxeo.apidoc.listener.contrib">

  <extension target="org.nuxeo.ecm.core.event.EventServiceComponent" point="listener">
    <listener name="latestDistributionsListener" async="false" postCommit="false"
      class="org.nuxeo.apidoc.listener.LatestDistributionsListener">
      <event>aboutToCreate</event>
      <event>beforeDocumentModification</event>
    </listener>

    <listener name="AttributesExtractorStater" async="false" postCommit="false"
      class="org.nuxeo.apidoc.listener.AttributesExtractorStater">
      <event>aboutToCreate</event>
      <event>beforeDocumentModification</event>
    </listener>

    <listener name="AttributesExtractorScheduler" async="false" postCommit="false"
      class="org.nuxeo.apidoc.listener.AttributesExtractorScheduler" priority="20">
      <event>documentCreated</event>
      <event>documentModified</event>
    </listener>
  </extension>


</component>
